Package: ctrlvee
Title: Extract External R Code and Insert Inline
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("VP", "Nagraj", email = "nagraj@nagraj.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An RStudio/Positron addin that prompts the user for a web URL,
    fetches the page content, extracts R code chunks, and inserts those code chunks
    into the active editor at the current cursor position. Supports extraction of raw Markdown/Quarto source files, GitHub Gists and rendered HTML pages that have pre/code elements
    with R-related classes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    rstudioapi,
    httr2,
    xml2,
    purrr,
    magrittr
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/vpnagraj/ctrlvee
BugReports: https://github.com/vpnagraj/ctrlvee/issues
